items.title: Free for Dev
items.content_text:
### DNS

*   [Dynv6.com](https://dynv6.com/) — Free DDNS service with [API support](https://dynv6.com/docs/apis) and management of a lot of dns record types (like CNAME, MX, SPF, SRV, TXT and others).
*   [noip.at](https://noip.at/) — Free DDNS service without registration, tracking, logging or advertising. No limit to domains.
items.content_html:

items.title: Awesome Gnome
items.content_text:
### System and Customization

*   [Embellish](https://flathub.org/apps/io.github.getnf.embellish) - Application to install and manage Nerd Fonts on the system.

### Development and Design

*   [Aurea](https://flathub.org/apps/io.github.cleomenezesjr.aurea) - Simple preview banner made to read metainfo files from Flatpak apps and represent them as they would on Flathub.
*   [Exhibit](https://flathub.org/apps/io.github.nokse22.Exhibit) - 3D model previewer based on the F3D library that supports many formats.
items.content_html:
System and Customization

  • Embellish - Application to install and manage Nerd Fonts on the system.

Development and Design

  • Aurea - Simple preview banner made to read metainfo files from Flatpak apps and represent them as they would on Flathub.
  • Exhibit - 3D model previewer based on the F3D library that supports many formats.
